# {{science}} A method of discovering [[knowledge]] in which [[observation]] of [[phenomena]] leads to the [[deduction]] of [[natural]] [[law]]s, and the [[formulation]] of [[hypotheses]] to make [[prediction]]s on previously unobserved phenomena; [[experiment]]s are [[constructed]] to [[demonstrate]] the [[truth]] or [[falseness]] of these hypotheses and laws which are [[validate]]d or [[modified]] according to the outcome.
